ygData.messageBody:
I did bootstrutters backpack quest at lvl 29 so I dont think there is a
level cap. Remember ONLY Duster X & V.. The cleaners will get you killed.
And BTW the guy who gives you the backpack after you have the two pieces is
across from the mines... swim across the water and he's there next to some
machine.. you can hail him. or just give him the pieces. BTW for you non
Enchanters, I "heard" there was a faction requirement but i'mm not sure. I
cast belevolence on him (+200 faction) and had no problems.. FYI

Countt
lvl 40 Enchanter Emarr
